# Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of up-to-date sources and the potential bias in interpretations of governmental power dynamics. Additionally, the complexity of the U.S. political system means that power can shift between branches depending on the political context and specific administrations. The findings are based on available data up to October 2023, and newer developments may not be reflected.